citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
An authorized person was not available to accompany USDA officials for an unannounced inspection at 5:05 pm on
March 23, 2023. We called the main facility contact person, leaving a voicemail message at 5:09pm and then 5:22PM.
We knocked on the doors of two residences at the addresses but persons at each door indicated they were not the
licensee. We waited at the property until 5:40pm.
Additional Inspectors:
SCOTT WELCH, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
